text: Benjamin Eberle (born 3 March 1963) is a Liechtenstein cross-country skier who competed in the 1988 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Liechtenstein male cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Liechtenstein Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1988 Winter Olympics
